Instead of using the next state literals fresh inputs (or otherwise
unused latches or gates) can be used to refrence the next-counter.
After introducing the 2 inputs everything is shifted.
Note that no literal mapping needs to be given explicitly as the
default (first n inputs and first m latches) is the desired one.